title: ÄIJÄ
overview: The comedy series ÄIJÄ begins when Tauno and his best friend Rasmus start seventh grade. Tauno realizes that he seems like a childish sissy compared to the others. He is in danger of becoming an unpopular outcast! Tauno starts a social media channel for dads and even changes his name, now Tauno is TJ. The goal is to get into the school's popular, tough gang of boys, who even hang out in the school attic - as long as Rasmus doesn't screw up the whole thing.
